      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i just got this prescription for zolpidem to help me sleep better cuz im having a hard time lately. i was wondering if its okay if i have a glass of wine with my dinner before i take it? i feel like the wine might actually help the pill work a bit faster so i can fall asleep quicker. is that fine?",
