      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that it can be \"risky\" but i'm not talking about getting wasted or anything, just like a single small glass of red wine with my meal. surely one glass won't actually kill me or anything? it just feels like a natural way to relax before the pill kicks in. wouldn't the alcohol just help settle my system so the zolpidem works more efficiently?",
